OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain, heavy at times, will move
OL,7,Fquickly eastwards across all areas
OL,8,Fthis evening. This clearing by dawn,
OL,9,Fwith clearer spells and drier
OL,10,Fconditions developing from the west.
OL,11,FWindy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA breezy day, although it
OL,14,Fshould be largely dry with bright or
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Chance of a few showers
OL,16,Freaching western parts later in the
OL,17,Fday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
