OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBlustery and largely dry Thursday,
OL,7,Fbefore a band of rain, heavy and
OL,8,Fsqually, moves erratically southeast
OL,9,Fovernight, clearing to blustery
OL,10,Fshowers Friday. Feeling colder. Drier,
OL,11,Fbrighter and less windy Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
